  high_ground: "**High Ground**: DM-dependent; some give +2 attack or advantage. RAW no bonus, but narrative positioning helps.",
  focus_fire: "**Focus Fire**: concentrate damage on one enemy to reduce enemy action economy. A dead enemy deals 0 damage.",
  action_economy: "**Action Economy**: your side's actions vs enemy actions. Winning means using bonus actions/reactions effectively.",
